title: Adobe CS6 Crack Assistant v1.0.1.0
description:
This tool was included in http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8632493/Adobe_CS6_Master_Collection along with the Adobe CS6 suite but has become upgraded to the point of becoming a separate project. This will automatically copy the necessary files to crack any installation of Adobe CS6. It's just one executable and that's all you need. The last version copied one file to the wrong places because of a setting needlessly being checked. This also adds command-line support (just use it from CMD like "acs6ca /?" to find out more) to allow for only certain programs being cracked. Enjoy! :)

P.S., I would appreciate it if someone else packaged and started seeding another CS6 Master Collection with this included.
